body_preview: Ref: https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/pull/63231#discussion_r2574423506  When a option is deprecated and a user uses a `pd.option_context` to modify the setting, the warning stacklevel using `find_stack_level()` points at contextlib rather than the user's calling code.
